{"tid":2487630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂台北8,000呎豪宅曝光、浴室面積超過200呎！網民狠批太空洞","createTime":"2021-04-13T16:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T22:20:58.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2e35f964a5851fb59f32f761152ae247047977","tid":2487630,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"余文樂近年順風順水，成功在兩岸三地密密吸金。17年與台灣籍妻子王棠云結婚後，幸福滿瀉三年抱兩，枝繁葉茂。余文樂早前於IG開心share同老婆耍花槍的影片，台北8千呎豪宅亦意外曝光。<br />\n<br />\n余文樂於17年迎娶台灣名媛王棠云後，積極造人，成功三年抱兩，先後誕下兒子余初見（Cody）及女兒余初心，決定要定居台灣的余文樂斥資近3億台幣（約7,700萬港元）購入台北豪宅「頂禾園」讓家人有個安樂窩！早前余文樂在IG story上載了惡搞太太王棠云的短片，兩公婆大耍花槍，豪宅內貌亦因此曝光。片中太太王棠云身處洗手間，可見面積極為寬敞，淋浴間跟廁所分開，設計同5星級酒店類似；冷色配合鏡面反光設計，令浴室空間感十足。目測浴室面積超過200呎，不少港人半間屋企咁大。<br />\n<br />\n余文樂自跟家人搬入台北約8,000呎豪宅，間唔中就在社交平台晒豪宅，逢年過節就會邀約朋友去佢屋企食飯作客，當中有不少都是圈中人，之前就有邀請彭于晏。<br />\n<br />\n婚後余文樂已經豪擲近8千萬港元，入手台北中正區「頂禾園」14樓，並順帶買埋樓下的6個車位。自去年新冠肺炎疫情肆虐，余文樂陪同妻兒留在台灣，期間仲有指余文樂在港賣出多架名車，套現走資去台灣做生意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXyeHMjefwRzZBwU1DcxBg9WF1DdxPE2bJQqbGX5tY7nv?filename=SFyuFze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFyuFze.jpg&h=4b08c14f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQtTMmTcTLmm918oxafiUH6HhtyZ89EyFPH5oGyKgNHHH?filename=qtSfA7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtSfA7A.jpg&h=75082788&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNdaKMz8qC8Puhf4ipeYg1KqqW1cCQTUDCTXUYHxuzU2e?filename=9ZMTnNB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZMTnNB.jpg&h=b7866f05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZeLNTbgTG25bLrPaxNeaQsWFfDRERbaJRFY8pXK9KXDN?filename=YujqdUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYujqdUh.jpg&h=65365df5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPTECJ5WmXa4g4RrSngtQGPRNCWW1hYJYVjHwm6DNLZRQ?filename=r6Bssei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6Bssei.jpg&h=8695adbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89ce6ea55cedceadfeacba72df520d6b405ff371","tid":2487630,"uid":43557,"like":106,"dislike":2,"score":104,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐 有冇佢老婆俾李宗瑞屌既片"},{"pid":"6ac71c7e865cb8df3e4130eb4cba825154028220","tid":2487630,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"初見初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a9bd81ef45c63428be53911383466de27a709f","tid":2487630,"uid":271485,"like":162,"dislike":2,"score":160,"quote":{"pid":"89ce6ea55cedceadfeacba72df520d6b405ff371","tid":2487630,"uid":43557,"like":106,"dislike":2,"score":104,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐 有冇佢老婆俾李宗瑞屌既片"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢果陣叫王予柔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRRArU7K1nT9pUoAo8S6WrEk977y23fzzRUNUyqYSKTdd?filename=2qq5dV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qq5dV2.jpg&h=801a73f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24137c7e63bdcf9ec843e5dc8464c10fd53da8b5","tid":2487630,"uid":43557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"96a9bd81ef45c63428be53911383466de27a709f","tid":2487630,"uid":271485,"like":162,"dislike":2,"score":160,"quote":{"pid":"89ce6ea55cedceadfeacba72df520d6b405ff371","tid":2487630,"uid":43557,"like":106,"dislike":2,"score":104,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐 有冇佢老婆俾李宗瑞屌既片"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢果陣叫王予柔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qq5dV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qq5dV2.jpg&h=801a73f3&s={